# Welcome to Out Of Space

![e09c83ac2723df416273595e6ede0f95.jpg](///raw/9e5/d/z/17b12.jpg)

![nom.png](///raw/9e5/d/z/17b3a.png)

### Play the game [here](https://zapphire-studios.itch.io/out-of-space)

#### Info About The Game
You are an astronaut, while working in your totally cool station you hear the monster crushing it's way through the building. You decide to leg it to the highway to earth before you become a crunchy snack, you have to run out of space!

The gameplay consist of you running down towards earth avoiding obstacles , holes and things that go crunch crunch munch munch.

#### About us
this is our second time working as a team, last time was a mess, but for now we are satisfied with this result. Our members were:

@blooobird : Level design, importing, colouring , testing and doing light work.

@totalaj : Doing the programming, level design and the amazing music and sound effects.

@dj-depressive : Our head of 3D creating the character, big monster and the earth itself and being a useful resource. 

@camerox : Creating loads of 3d props.

@milleost : Prooops and a few bugs.

@battiefrog : A few props.

@karin-g : 2d stuffs, concepts and a bit of 3d and the design of the terrifying monster.

@tick : 2d stuffs and the great character design.

